text: Labidura is a genus of earwigs in the family Labiduridae. ==Species== The genus contains the following species: * Labidura cryptera Liu, 1946 * Labidura dharchulensis Gangola, 1968 * Labidura elegans Liu, 1946 * Labidura japonica (Haan, 1842) * Labidura minor Boeseman, 1954 * Labidura orientalis Steinmann, 1979 * Labidura riparia (Pallas, 1773) * Labidura xanthopus (Stal, 1855) * Labidura herculeana (Fabricius, 1798) ==References== Category:Earwigs Category:Dermaptera genera Category:Taxa named by William Elford Leach
title: Labidura
